{"tid":2199829,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭係需要付出成本","createTime":"2020-09-12T13:18:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T13:17:55.000Z","uid":228436,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"dc8420a33bef46097621417036ad5448066c8b1c","tid":2199829,"uid":228436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:18:16.000Z","msg":"利申：唔係想分化 唔係想鬥黃<br />\n黃嘅光譜好大 無絕對嘅對錯<br />\n我講嘅只係我個人感受<br />\n雖然有啲長 但係都希望有人陪我傾下計<br />\n歡迎理性討論但勿批鬥<br />\n<br />\n係連登<br />\n如果有人post話食M記<br />\n留言好快話「屌你仲食M記」<br />\n但係係現實世界<br />\nM記一出優惠就排曬長龍<br />\n又或者係Ig share話自己今日食M記全餐<br />\n<br />\n然後睇到呢啲應該就有啲聲稱自己係前線勇武嘅話<br />\n：「我打狗之後食M記居然比人話偽黃」<br />\n：「無錢呀嘛 就要食M記㗎啦」<br />\n<br />\n先唔講幾多真係前線勇武定係係五毛<br />\n但係其實我唔係針對食M記呢個行為咁簡單<br />\n<span class=\"red\">係想針對唔食M記背後嘅行為成本</span><br />\n<br />\n人人都知道完全戒中資係幾咁難<br />\n講水/菜/豬肉其實都其實99.9999%人都係「偽黃」<br />\n唔係話唔可以用高成本買外國產品（記住係包括水）<br />\n但係其實無人會咁做<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">想講嘅就係「成本」問題</span><br />\n<br />\n用水呢個例子講成本的話<br />\n基本上無人會買外國食水去沖涼<br />\n無人會反對「逼於無奈」地用東江水沖涼<br />\n<br />\n但係講到食M記呢個例子<br />\n個爭議性就比較大<br />\n最常見係「有人會話買少個餐對佢影響有幾大？」「做黎都無用㗎啦」<br />\n然後啲人就真係繼續幫襯M記<br />\n繼續俾錢M記賺<br />\n另外一方面又有人話<br />\n「M記啲漢堡包先十幾蚊 黃店起碼一倍以上」<br />\n然後類似呢啲<span class=\"red\">太貴/太遠/太麻煩呢啲理由</span>就出咗黎<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係 呢啲都係成本之一<br />\n包括最易計算嘅金錢成本<br />\n又或者係時間成本等等<br />\n甚至前線抗爭嘅付出自己嘅未來<br />\n每一次行動都係拎將來做成本<br />\n<br />\n每個人可以付出嘅成本極限都唔同<br />\n<span class=\"red\">再次強調我唔係想鬥每個人可以付出到幾多成本</span><br />\n同埋其實點鬥都鬥唔過啲流亡海外嘅手足<br />\n佢地無家人無朋友係佢地身旁<br />\n更加面對不知去向嘅將來<br />\n佢地先係付出最大個個<br />\n<br />\n返返去付出幾多成本呢個問題<br />\n其實係咪少少成本都付出唔到呢<br />\n<br />\n好多香港人貪快貪方便貪平繼續搭黨鐵<br />\n但係831就會記得係IG share文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能佢地覺得唔會係覺得自己share人地嘅文宣post就係自己極限成本呀嘛？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實可以做嘅嘢更加多<br />\n出門口揀搭巴士其實就已經行多咗步<br />\n但係只係因為懶而唔做<br />\n我好想同佢地講一句<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">抗爭係需要付出成本</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同埋想講<br />\n香港人真係好有錢<br />\n我地好難去到烏克蘭咁嘅程度<br />\n但係同時我地用嘅抗爭手法都俾其他人多<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">香港人 唔好放棄住啦好無 唔好俾班放負撚睇死啦好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n講到呢度 都覺得自己1999<br />\n唉 唔講咁多啦<br />\n最後：<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"xx-large\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef391a40544a9f7c8423630b1f0346d632d9e198","tid":2199829,"uid":228436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:20:08.000Z","msg":"其實係俾我個fd激親<br />\n今日見到佢post IG Story係度拆淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係度慳少少錢然後係度買垃圾"},{"pid":"899cbae01c894f9e754568e68f53bda037b848b1","tid":2199829,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"blue\"></span>"},{"pid":"c48dd9e5067675bfd509053acce0d90627602e0a","tid":2199829,"uid":228436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:22:41.000Z","msg":"基本上無人會反對用高成本（東江水）取代超高成本（外國食水）<br />\n唔係話唔討論本地集水/海水化淡<br />\n只係想集中討論現階段香港人可以做到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79661f185dc16ab79f3b57b79d1b605a941c071c","tid":2199829,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6f59722bcde54eea53528036361db5ed7c799bc","tid":2199829,"uid":339751,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔需要咁樣鬥黃<br />\n每用100幫襯呢啲藍店/紅店<br />\n咪用返200去幫襯黃店囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1a1a84edb11339bf7b3908519e5923f8749f5a","tid":2199829,"uid":294797,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:29:17.000Z","msg":"我就堅持自己理念，<br />\n冇幫襯食 M記、美心、大家樂年幾，<br />\n做得幾多得幾多，身邊人感化幾多得幾多，<br />\n好多人的確以方便或價錢為先，都無辦法<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1639038e357c3fc1f424beb51028af0396a038ff","tid":2199829,"uid":55089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:38:36.000Z","msg":"做好自己就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9587bb3927769685f068d0408ff3c3c76cfd9992","tid":2199829,"uid":228436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:39:45.000Z","msg":"有時做Twitter/Reddit見到無咩人都有啲灰心<br />\n自己成日都問自己係咪真係有用<br />\n其實日日出tweet其實都無人睇<br />\n跟著成日都想上連登呻<br />\n但係又怕比人鬧係放負撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日真係忍唔住<br />\n做一次放負撚 sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9351bedaf6cdf0bdb474e2b671866d808047f539","tid":2199829,"uid":228436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6f59722bcde54eea53528036361db5ed7c799bc","tid":2199829,"uid":339751,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:27:16.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔需要咁樣鬥黃<br />\n每用100幫襯呢啲藍店/紅店<br />\n咪用返200去幫襯黃店囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:45:39.000Z","msg":"都唔係鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係想叫大家行多一步<br />\n去付出能力範圍內嘅抗爭成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f1cea98f807b64915fe6765b68e623e0ce5673","tid":2199829,"uid":311837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"其實仲有個問題係合理替代品<br />\n相若價錢下，有無其他黃 / 外資選擇<br />\n而個個人嘅錢就有限嘅（upper bound 係收入，人工唔會個個月加），時間亦有限"},{"pid":"c529c53c156d277b65269689c4d37f38575d887b","tid":2199829,"uid":228436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9f1cea98f807b64915fe6765b68e623e0ce5673","tid":2199829,"uid":311837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"其實仲有個問題係合理替代品<br />\n相若價錢下，有無其他黃 / 外資選擇<br />\n而個個人嘅錢就有限嘅（upper bound 係收入，人工唔會個個月加），時間亦有限"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T14:01:47.000Z","msg":"呢個terms好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能係我表達得唔好<br />\n其實我想表達嘅就係想叫人去用多啲合理代替品<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日聽「吓 我唔識搭巴士去xx 都係搭地鐵方便啲」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a058e6617dbcd40262833378c665b57da14ac913","tid":2199829,"uid":311837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c529c53c156d277b65269689c4d37f38575d887b","tid":2199829,"uid":228436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9f1cea98f807b64915fe6765b68e623e0ce5673","tid":2199829,"uid":311837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-12T13:55:41.000Z","msg":"其實仲有個問題係合理替代品<br />\n相若價錢下，有無其他黃 / 外資選擇<br />\n而個個人嘅錢就有限嘅（upper 